	//x[posindex]ã®ä½ç½®ã«ã¤ã„ãŸç›´å¾Œã§ã€è‡ªåˆ†ã‚ˆã‚Šæ‰‹å‰ã®ç†Šã¯å‡¦ç†æ¸ˆã¿ã§ã€è‡ªåˆ†ã‚ˆã‚Šå¥¥ã®ç†Šã¯æ‰‹ä»˜ã‹ãš

	if (posindex == N)return 0;
	if (memo[posindex] != -1)return memo[posindex];

	int ans = intmax;

	//ãã®å ´ã§å¾…ã¤
	ans = min(ans, solve(posindex + 1) + T + x[posindex + 1] - x[posindex]);

	//å…ˆã¾ã§è¡Œã
	REP(i, posindex+1, N) {
		int sol = solve(i + 1);
		int dist = x[i] - x[posindex];
		int gets = max(T + dist, dist * 3);
		int res = sol + gets + x[i + 1] - x[i];
		if (ans < res)break;
		ans = res;
	}
	memo[posindex] = ans;
	return ans;
}

